Conferences
 
September 27, 20172017 Digital Banking SummitToronto, Canada 








Financial Sponsors


 


Our dedicated professionals bring forth the full resources of the investment and corporate bank to provide financial sponsors solutions throughout the entire lifecycle of their investments, including idea generation, acquisition, holding period, and liquidity events.
 
Our financial sponsor loan program gives private equity firms a fast, flexible and convenient means to access capital, without tapping the resources of limited partners. Credit facilities, underwritten on a fund's committed capital and quality of its limited partner investors, are available for short-term and long-term applications.


Contact info
 
U.S.: +1 212 885 4000








Food, Consumer & Retail


 


For more than 80 years, BMO Capital Markets has committed broad resources to helping companies across the food, consumer and retail sectors. Consisting of more than 35 professionals, the Food, Consumer & Retail group provides merger and acquisition advice, capital raising and value-added ideas through their industry expertise.
 
Sector specialization:
 

Agriculture
Consumer Products
Food & Beverage
Food Distribution




Pet Food & Products
Protein
Restaurants
Retail

 
Contact info
 
U.S.: +1 312 461 2244


Conferences
 
There are no current conferences for this industry.








Global Energy


 


In the volatile energy market, you need an advisor with experience to help turn bright ideas into powerful results. BMO Capital Markets has over 100 years of experience working with the energy industry – more than a century of fueling global growth for ambitious companies. Whether your firm operates upstream, midstream or downstream, we can help you achieve your ambitions.
 
Sector specialization:
 

Acquisition & Divestiture
Distribution
Exploration & production
Generation
Income funds & trusts
Master limited partnerships
Oilfield services
Pipelines & diversified energy



Newsletters
 
U.S. Oil & Gas Bi-Weekly Update: our bi-weekly e-newsletter is a wrap-up of capital markets activity and industry news.
 
Subscribe now
 
 
Contact info
 
Canada: +1 403 515 1516U.S.: +1 713 223 4400EMEA: +44 20 7236 1010


Conferences
 
October 4 - 5, 20172017 Canadian High Yield Dinner & ConferenceToronto, Ontario 








Global Metals & Mining


 


BMO Capital Markets has more than a century of service to the metals and mining sector, giving us the deep-set expertise needed to help large and middle-market companies in their search for growth.
 
Capabilities:
 

An integrated team of mining engineers, geologists and financial professionals in Toronto, Vancouver, Chicago, New York, London, Melbourne and Beijing
An industry-leading underwriter of equity issues for mining companies
A top M&A advisor to North American metals & mining companies
Derivatives strategies that use physical metal to hedge commodity exposures




Hosts of the world's top Global Metals & Mining investor conference
One of the world's largest mining research groups, covering 130+ metals, mining and fertilizer stocks



Global Metals & Mining brochure (4.32MB, PDF)

 
 
