Real Estate


 


Real estate is a competitive, transaction-intensive business. The  BMO Capital Markets team of dedicated Real Estate professionals understands the nuances of the market and  thinks creatively to help our clients execute transactions. This enables them to navigate emerging opportunities, from strategic M&A to realigning their capital structure. Working across North America on transactions of all sizes, our team delivers a leading, full-service real estate platform to a broad base of public and private clients. Our financial expertise, knowledge of local markets and seamless execution will help put your company's future on a solid foundation.
 
Sector Specialization:
 

Retail
Office
Industrial
Multi-family residential
Lodging & Leisure
Manufactured Housing
Medical Office
Net Lease
Self-storage
Senior housing




Property Brokerage and Advisory
            
Buy-side advisory
Debt placement
Fairness opinions
Valuations



 
