Capital Raising
 
 


Access to capital is critical to your company's business strategy. Whether you're looking to finance an acquisition or bolster liquidity, we can open the door to global capital markets. We have decades of experience raising capital for high-grade corporate and public issuers in Canada, and a growing volume of high-yield issuances and private placements in the U.S. Our broad array of financing solutions ranges from traditional loans and commitments to complex structured financing.
 


Capabilities:
 

Access to hybrid corporate securities, special-purpose securities and derivative strategies
Unparalleled sales and trading capabilities
Public equity transactions on guaranteed/bought deal basis in U.S.
Ability to transact in various currencies at fixed or floating rates
Flexible, stratified debt structures 
Fixed income market coverage
